<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-1957] NodeJS TFramedTransport and TBufferedTransport read bytes as unsigned</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1957</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Thrift for NodeJS is reading bytes as unsigned. The Apache Thrift specification describes them as signed. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I changed the readByte function in both TFramedTransport and TBufferedTransport to call a new readByte method in binary.js that properly converts to a signed byte. Unit test for the method is included in binary.test.js&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;NodeJS 10.4, Thrift 0.9&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
